{"_path":"/the_rocket_scientist","_dir":"","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"火箭科学家","description":"John Carmack，出生于天主教家庭的他天生智力非凡，而父母的过分管教导致了他的叛逆。机缘巧合下，他早早的接触到了 BBS 社区，为了买到自己的第一台电脑，他从上面学会了制作炸药来卖钱，他也因此进入了少管所。此后，这个少年天才兼少年犯在经历家庭破碎、经济困难后，仍然孤注一掷的踏上了游戏开发之路……","navigation":false,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":"doom, book, translation"},{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"},{"name":"author","content":"tyyuan"}]},"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"chapter-header","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"第二章：火箭科学家"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"John Carmack 很晚才学会说话。\n他的父母一直为此担心，直到 1971 的一天，15 个月大的 Carmack 摇摇晃晃的走进客厅，一手举着海绵，说：“这是你的丝瓜络，爸爸”。这感觉就像是，之前他不说话只是因为不想颠三倒四地说单词，而是想等着能通顺说句子后才张的口。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"“Inga（母亲名字）”，孩子的父亲 Stan 对他的妻子说，“或许，咱家的宝贝超乎寻常。”"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Carmack 身处一个自学成才的家庭中。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"doing","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"hr","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开始翻译于2024.06.05"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"prev-next","props":{},"children":[]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:5.the_rocket_scientist.md","_source":"content","_file":"5.the_rocket_scientist.md","_extension":"md"}